One person has been killed and two others injured after twin attacks in the Kerio Valley at the weekend. On Friday, two Pokot boys were attacked and injured in Akiriamet, West Pokot, by suspected Marakwet bandits.In retaliation, Pokots raided Lukuget, Marakwet East, where they shot dead a 22-year-old man on Saturday night.Stephen Kipchumba died on the spot when he was shot in the neck.